17 or other locations as provided for in Code Section 21-2-382 shall, upon request to a
18 designated office employee or other individual, be authorized to vote immediately at the
19 next available voting compartment or booth without having to wait in line if such location
20 utilizes direct recording electronic voting systems or be authorized to go to the head of any
